                <p style="font-size: normal;text-align: left;line-height: 25px;">  
                    <h5 style="text-align: left; font-weight:bold;"># What types of data does Nature's Palette accept?</h5>
                    <p style="text-align: left"> For now, the repository only accepts reflectance data (relative radiance) taken from plants and animals either 
                    from museum specimens or from field data collection. Eventually, the repository will also accept irradiance measurements from natural sources 
                    and the transmission properties of natural substrates.
                    </p>
